\c 13
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukusizwa
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Koze kube nini, N\nd kosi\nd*, ungikhohlwa\x + Hlab. 79.5. 89.46.\x* kokuphela\x + Hlab. 79.5. 89.46.\x*? Koze kube nini ungifihlela ubuso bakho\x + Jobe 13.24. Hlab. 89.46.\x*?
\v 2 Koze kube nini ngizicebisa emphefumulweni wami, \add ngilo\add*sizi enhliziyweni yami insuku zonke? Koze kube nini isitha sami siphakanyiswa phezu kwami?
\v 3 Khangela, ungiphendule, N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wami; khanyisa amehlo ami\x + Ezra 9.8. Hlab. 19.8. 1 Sam. 14.27.\x* hlezi ngilale ubuthongo bokufa\x + Jer. 51.39.\x*,
\v 4 hlezi isitha sami sithi: \add Se\add*ngimehlule\x + Hlab. 25.2. 30.1. 35.19,24. 38.16.\x*; \add l\add*abangihluphayo bathokoze lapho nginyikinywa\x + Hlab. 10.6.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa mina ngithembele emuseni wakho\x + Hlab. 28.7. 33.21. Hlab. 25.2.\x*, inhliziyo yami izathaba ngosindiso lwakho\x + Hlab. 9.14.\x*\x + Hlab. 28.7. 33.21. Hlab. 25.2.\x*.
\v 6 Ngizayihlabelela iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba ingenzele okuhle kakhulu\x + Hlab. 103.10. 116.7. 119.17. 142.7.\x*.